# ── Schemas (JSON Schema, draft-07 subset) ───────────────────────────────
#
# Single source of truth for all LINCE config validation (#203, design:
# docs/design/config-v2-design.md §2/§3). The files under schemas/ in the
# repo are generated from these via `lince-config schema --write schemas/`
# and are Taplo-compatible — point your TOML editor/LSP at them for
# autocomplete and inline validation. A repo test asserts no drift.
#
# Validation policy (§2.1 forward-compat): unknown keys under known tables
# are WARNINGS (warn-and-ignore); type mismatches and missing required keys
# are ERRORS. Keys under [experimental] are never errors.

